
1) Extract source from tarball
2) Configure for all three arches:
	SnowLeopard General: --prefix="/usr" --openssldir="/System/Library/OpenSSL" threads shared zlib no-hw no-idea enable-rc5 enable-mdc2 enable-seed
	SnowLeopard arches : darwin-i386-llvm darwin64-x84_64-llvm darwin-ppc-llvm
3) Update opensslconf.h
4) Update MacOS/buildinf.h

Places to updated when the version changes:
* "Install pkgconfig" build phase
* "Install Open Source License" build phase
* "Install Open Source Version" build phase

